OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780416668
OL,3,C'Talented' 11-year-old football
OL,4,Ccaptain dies five months after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FAn 11-year-old football captain
OL,8,Fdescribed as "full of life, talent and
OL,9,Fjoy" has died five months after a
OL,10,Fdevastating house fire destroyed his
OL,11,Fhome.
OL,13,FCole, who was part of the under-12s
OL,14,Fteam at Charnock Richard FC, died on
OL,15,FFriday, 29 May, after he was
OL,16,Fcritically injured in the blaze in
OL,17,FClayton Green, near Chorley,
OL,18,FLancashire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
