FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780416668
OL,3,C'Talented' 11-year-old football
OL,4,Ccaptain dies five months after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FEmergency services rushed to the
OL,8,Fsevere blaze in Greenwood shortly
OL,9,Fbefore midnight on 6 January 2026.
OL,11,FCole and his mother, Kim Leighton,
OL,12,Fwere rescued from the property but
OL,13,Fwere left in a critical condition in
OL,14,FManchester Children's Hospital and
OL,15,FWythenshawe Hospital.
OL,17,FFollowing the news of Cole's death,
OL,18,FCharnock Richard FC released a
OL,19,Fstatement on social media paying
OL,20,Ftribute to their young captain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
