OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780416668
OL,3,C'Talented' 11-year-old football
OL,4,Ccaptain dies five months after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FThe club said: "It is with the
OL,8,Fheaviest of hearts that everyone at
OL,9,FCharnock Richard FC learns of the
OL,10,Fdevastating passing of our under 12s
OL,11,Fcaptain, Cole.
OL,13,F"Cole had been a part of our club
OL,14,Fsince he was just four years old,
OL,15,Fgrowing up alongside his teammates and
OL,16,Fcapturing the hearts of everyone who
OL,17,Fknew him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780416668
OL,3,C'Talented' 11-year-old football
OL,4,Ccaptain dies five months after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,F"There are no words to adequately
OL,8,Fexpress the grief we are all feeling.
OL,9,FHe was a true leader on and off the
OL,10,Fpitch and a much-loved member of our
OL,11,Ffootball family ` full of life, talent
OL,12,Fand joy. His loss leaves a profound
OL,13,Fvoid in our club."
OL,15,FThey added that their "thoughts,
OL,16,Fprayers, and deepest condolences" are
OL,17,Fwith Cole's mother Kim, his dad Craig,
OL,18,Fand all of his extended family,
OL,19,Ffriends, and teammates.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780416668
OL,3,C'Talented' 11-year-old football
OL,4,Ccaptain dies five months after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,F"As a club, we are a community, and we
OL,8,Fwill stand together to support Kim,
OL,9,FCraig, Cole's teammates and everyone
OL,10,Faffected in any way we can as we
OL,11,Fnavigate this immense loss together.
OL,12,FRest in peace, Captain Cole."
OL,14,FFollowing extensive enquiries into the
OL,15,Fblaze, Lancashire Police reported in
OL,16,FFebruary that there was "no criminal
OL,17,Felement" to the incident.
OL,18,FInvestigators concluded that the fire
OL,19,Fwas likely accidental.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
