FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780416668
OL,3,C'Talented' 11-year-old football
OL,4,Ccaptain dies five months after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FThe local community has rallied behind
OL,8,Fthe family, who lost all of their
OL,9,Fbelongings in the fire. A GoFundMe
OL,10,Fpage launched to support them during
OL,11,Ftheir recovery and hospital stay has
OL,12,Fraised more than #32,000.
OL,14,FAnother fundraising page has been set
OL,15,Fup since Cole's death to help with
OL,16,Ffuneral costs. It says: "After 21
OL,17,Fweeks and 3 days of fighting Cole
OL,18,Funfortunately has very sadly passed
OL,19,Faway.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
