CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780416668
OL,3,C'Talented' 11-year-old football
OL,4,Ccaptain dies five months after house
OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,F"He fought so hard right until the
OL,8,Fvery end. His family & friends are all
OL,9,Fabsolutely devastated. I'm setting up
OL,10,Fthis page for people to donate big or
OL,11,Fsmall , in the hope it will bring some
OL,12,Fcomfort to his loved ones , to be able
OL,13,Fto give cole the most amazing send of
OL,14,Fever like he deserves.
OL,16,F"Forever 11 Cole".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
